snippet.title: Little Nightmares II Enhanced Edition - Comparative Trailer
snippet.description: Dive even deeper into a world of charming horror with Little Nightmares II, now enhanced in mesmerizing 4K with improved visual effects! This beautiful upgrade for next-gen hardware will release for the first time in physical version on PS5 on Friday, 25 October 2024!
